      <guid>https://example.com/project/pytorch/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a basic HMM-based ASR that uses MFCC and delta features to identify six phrases: &amp;ldquo;Odessa&amp;rdquo; (a keyword phrase), &amp;ldquo;Play music,&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;Start music,&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;Turn off the lights,&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;Turn on the lights,&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;What time is it.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
